        Changelog
        =========
        
        2.5+rl0
        -------
        
        - Incorporate support for PostgreSQL 13 and connection strings in environment.
        
        - Fix deprecation warning.
        
        
        2.4.6
        -------------------
        
        - Added all the supported isolation level options
        - Fixed pool bugs (psycopg issues #123, #125, #142)
        
        
        2.4.4
        -------------------
        
        - Make this and egg.
        
        
